== 歷史 ==
迪倫·菲爾德（Dylan Field）和埃文·華萊士（Evan Wallace）於 2012 年開始著手開發 Figma。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Figma gets $40 million Series C to put design tools in the cloud|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2019/02/14/figma-gets-40-million-series-c-to-put-design-tools-in-the-cloud/|accessdate=2020-11-15|author=Crook|date=2019-02-15|first=Jordan|work=TechCrunch|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107231140/https://techcrunch.com/2019/02/14/figma-gets-40-million-series-c-to-put-design-tools-in-the-cloud/|archivedate=2020-11-07}}</ref>這種基於Web的設計工具是菲爾德和華萊士在2011年就讀於[[布朗大学|布朗大學]]期間所構思的。2012年，華萊士從布朗大學畢業，而菲爾德則退學接受了[[泰爾獎學金|泰爾獎學金]]（Thiel Fellowship），該獎學金提供了10萬美元用於尋求創業想法。隨後，兩人移居到[[旧金山|舊金山]]，全職投入Figma的工作。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Why Teams at Uber and Slack Use This Powerful Design Tool|url=https://www.inc.com/michelle-cheng/figma-design-cloud-collaboration-google-docs-30-under-30-2019.html|accessdate=2020-11-15|author=Cheng|date=2019-04-18|first=Michelle|work=Inc.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127221649/https://www.inc.com/michelle-cheng/figma-design-cloud-collaboration-google-docs-30-under-30-2019.html}}</ref>

Figma從2015年12月3日開始提供採用邀請模式的免費預覽程式，<ref>{{Cite web|title=23-Year-Old’s Design Collaboration Tool Figma Launches With $14M To Fight Adobe|url=https://techcrunch.com/2015/12/03/figma-vs-goliath/|accessdate=2020-06-01|author=Constine|first=Josh|work=TechCrunch|publisher=TechCrunch|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102204308/https://techcrunch.com/2015/12/03/figma-vs-goliath/}}</ref>於2016年9月27日首次公開。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Figma Releases: Figma 1.0.0|url=https://releases.figma.com/2016/09/figma-100.html|accessdate=2020-06-01|work=Figma|archive-date=2016-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001035829/https://releases.figma.com/2016/09/figma-100.html}}</ref>

在2019年10月22日，Figma推出了Figma社群<ref>{{Cite web|title=Figma’s new community profiles let users view and remix design files|url=https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/22/20920929/figma-community-profiles-collaborative-design-beta|accessdate=2020-06-01|author=Lee|first=Dami|work=The Verge|publisher=The Verge|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421161607/https://www.theverge.com/2019/10/22/20920929/figma-community-profiles-collaborative-design-beta}}</ref>，允許設計師發布其作品供他人查看和修改。

2020年4月30日，D轮融资，Figma公司获得 Andreessen Horowitz 领投，Index Ventures、Greylock、Sequoia Capital、Kleiner Perkins等跟投的5000万美元资金。估值超过20亿美金<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/figma.html |title=多人协作界面设计工具独角兽：Figma Inc. |publisher=美股之家 |date=2021-04-18 |access-date=2021-04-19 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422162026/https://www.mg21.com/figma.html }}</ref>。截至2020年4月，Figma的估值超過20億美元。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Konrad|first=Alex|date=2020-04-30|title=Figma Eyes Acquisitions, New Tools With $50 Million In Fresh Funding At $2 Billion Valuation|work=Forbes|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/alexkonrad/2020/04/30/figma-raises-funding-eyes-acquisitions/#240c6b2211ea|accessdate=2021-03-25|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115074846/https://www.forbes.com/sites/alexkonrad/2020/04/30/figma-raises-funding-eyes-acquisitions/?sh=7ca9a2d711ea#240c6b2211ea}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Figma|url=https://growjo.com/company/Figma|accessdate=2020-11-19|work=Growjo|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128001438/https://growjo.com/company/Figma}}</ref>

2022年3月，Figma封停了[[大疆|大疆]]的账号。<ref>{{cite news |title=大疆突遭美国设计软件Figma“断供” 业内人士：国外企业把持市场 但替代难度不大 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2022-03-14/doc-imcwiwss6018997.shtml |accessdate=2022-03-15 |archive-date=2022-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316110017/https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2022-03-14/doc-imcwiwss6018997.shtml }}</ref>

